    <item>
      <title>日元集会，日本债券激增，而股票对关税的关税低迷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/yen-outperforms-major-peers-as-trump-tariffs-fuel-haven-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日元周四的日元表现优于其所有10个同行，而日本债券在最新的美国关税宣布提高了避风港的需求之后集会。东京的股票在主要亚洲市场中的股票下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/yen-outperforms-major-peers-as-trump-tariffs-fuel-haven-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 22:48:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国不包括钢，铝，黄金来自相互关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/us-excludes-steel-aluminum-copper-gold-from-reciprocal-tariff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫周三表示，钢铁，铝和一长串其他金属不会受到“互惠”关税的限制，此举为国内买家提供了救济，并建议政府对美国非常依赖进口商品的商品行事。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/us-excludes-steel-aluminum-copper-gold-from-reciprocal-tariff</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 21:43:02 GMT</pubDate>
